script.name: !lib.menu.mining
script.sourceplaintext:
$settings.table = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='egosoft.mine.auto' $Page.ID = 6020
if $a.state == [MEvent.Start] if not $settings.table $settings.table = table alloc $a.obj ->set local variable: name='egosoft.mine.auto' value=$settings.table $settings.table['maxrange'] = 9 $settings.table['maxmove'] = 5 $settings.table[Nividium] = 1 end
gosub sub.CreateMenu return $input
else if $a.state == 'menu' $selection = $a.value[0] if $selection -> exists $settings.table['sector'] = $selection return [TRUE] end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Arguments] $sector = $settings.table['sector'] gosub sub.GetMinerals $array = array alloc: size=0 $i = size of array $aMinerals while $i dec $i = $mineral = $aMinerals[$i] skip if $settings.table[$mineral] append $mineral to array $array end $maxmove = $settings.table['maxmove'] $maxrange = $settings.table['maxrange'] if $a.dropoff $dropoff = $settings.table['dropoff'] do if $dropoff $dropoff = get keys: table=$dropoff $ret = create new array, arguments=$sector, $array, $dropoff, $maxrange, $maxmove else $ret = create new array, arguments=$sector, $array, $maxrange, $maxmove, null end return $ret
else if $a.state == 'add.new' gosub sub.GetNewDropoff return $input
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Returned] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $state = $a.value[1] $selection = $a.value[2] if $menu.id == 'menu' if $state == 'dropoff' if $selection -> exists $table = $settings.table['dropoff'] $table[$selection] = $selection gosub sub.CreateMenu
return $menu end else if $state == 'select.sector' if $selection -> exists $input = create menu return to previous menu: value=$selection return $input end end end
else if $a.state == 'sector' $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2099 $input = create input: id='select.sector', user input=Var/Sector, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'hotkey' $menu.id = $a.value[0] $state = $a.value[1] $selection = $a.value[2] $value = convert serialised string to object: string=$selection if $value -> exists if $state == 'info' $type = $value -> get ware type code of object $input = create input: id='drop.detail' encyclopedia page, ware=$type return $input else if $state == 'detail' $input = create input: id='drop.info' object info page, object=$value return $input end end
else if $a.state == 'contextmenu' $table = $settings.table['dropoff'] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $state = $a.value[1] $selection = $a.value[2] $value = convert serialised string to object: string=$state if $value -> exists if $selection == 'remove' remove key $value from table $table gosub sub.CreateMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $selection == 'detail' $input = create input: id='drop.info' object info page, object=$value return $input else if $selection == 'info' $type = $value -> get ware type code of object $input = create input: id='drop.detail' encyclopedia page, ware=$type return $input else if $selection == 'clear' clear table $table gosub sub.CreateMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end end
else if $a.state == 'switch' $menu.id = $a.value[0] $state = $a.value[1] $selection = $a.value[2] if $menu.id == 'menu' $settings.table[$state] = $selection gosub sub.CreateMenu return $menu end end
return null
sub.CreateMenu: $done.sectors = table alloc gosub sub.GetMinerals
$menu = create custom menu array $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104260 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text $text = get command info: command=$a.cmd add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text
set menu option: $menu, icon=7 set menu option: $menu, maximum infolines=14 set menu option: $menu, global hotkey=[Key.Identity], id='info' set menu option: $menu, global hotkey=[Key.Details], id='detail'
gosub sub.JumpArray $jumps = $settings.table['maxrange'] $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2104 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$text, value array=$aValues, default=$jumps, return id='maxrange', width=100 allowtabs=[FALSE] $jumps = $settings.table['maxmove'] $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2105 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$text, value array=$aValues, default=$jumps, return id='maxmove', width=100 allowtabs=[FALSE]
$text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2106 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text $text = read text: page=1900 id=360 $text2 = read text: page=1900 id=361 $aValues = create new array, arguments=$text, $text2, null, null, null $size = size of array $aMinerals $any.minerals = [FALSE] $i = 0 while $i < $size $value = $aMinerals[$i] gosub sub.DrawMineral skip if $default $any.minerals = [TRUE] inc $i = end
if not $any.minerals $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2103 add info line section to menu: $menu add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text end
if $a.dropoff $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2107 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2108 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='add.new' value=null gosub sub.GetSortedValidDropoff if size of array $array add section to custom menu: $menu $size = size of array $array $i = 0 while $i < $size $value = $array[$i] $context = create context menu $serial = $value -> serialise object $ret = create menu return value: context menu, id=$serial, menu=$context, dynamic=[FALSE] $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=812 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$text, icon=29, returnvalue='info', hotkey=[Key.Identity], disabled=[FALSE] $text = read text: page=[Page.QMenus] id=60301 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$text, icon=20, returnvalue='detail', hotkey=[Key.Details], disabled=[FALSE] add context menu separator: menu=$context $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1107 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$text, icon=66, returnvalue='remove', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2109 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$text, icon=66, returnvalue='clear', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] $name = $value -> get name if $value -> is of class Station $text = read text: page=2006 id=2016 else $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=721 end add context menu global info line: menu=$context, name=$text, value=$name $name = $value -> get sector $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=715 add context menu global info line: menu=$context, name=$text, value=$name
if $value -> is docking possible of $a.obj $name = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=823 else if $value -> get amount of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay $name = sprintf: fmt='%s', Transporter Device, null, null, null, null else if $a.obj -> get amount of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay $name = sprintf: fmt='%s', Transporter Device, null, null, null, null else if $value -> get amount of ware Freight Drone in cargo bay $name = sprintf: fmt='%s', Freight Drone, null, null, null, null else if $a.obj -> get amount of ware Freight Drone in cargo bay $name = sprintf: fmt='%s', Freight Drone, null, null, null, null else $name = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2112 end $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2110 add context menu global info line: menu=$context, name=$text, value=$name
$text = $value -> get name $columns = array alloc: size=3 $text = $value ->create custom menu string object icon $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $columns[0] = $text $text = $value -> get name $text = create custom menu column string, position=10 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $columns[1] = $text $text = $value -> get sector $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $columns[2] = $text add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$columns returnvalue=$ret inc $i = end end end
if $a.sell end
$text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2111 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text
$sector = $settings.table['sector'] if $sector -> exists $text = sprintf: pageid=$Page.ID textid=255, $sector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$sector $done.sectors[$sector] = [TRUE] end $sector = $a.obj -> get sector if not $done.sectors[$sector] $text = sprintf: pageid=$Page.ID textid=254, $sector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$sector $done.sectors[$sector] = [TRUE] end $sector = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get sector if not $done.sectors[$sector] $text = sprintf: pageid=$Page.ID textid=210, $sector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$sector $done.sectors[$sector] = [TRUE] end $homebase = $a.obj -> get homebase if $homebase -> exists $sector = $homebase -> get sector if not $done.sectors[$sector] $text = sprintf: pageid=$Page.ID textid=227, $sector, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$sector $done.sectors[$sector] = [TRUE] end end
add section to custom menu: $menu $text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=212 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='sector' value=null
$text = get command name: command=$a.cmd $input = create input: id='menu' menu=$menu title=$text description=$a.obj callback=[Callback.Switch] endsub
sub.GetNewDropoff: $menu = create custom menu array $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9104 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text set menu option: $menu, icon=21 $stations = get station array: of race Player class/type=Dock gosub sub.FilterValidStations gosub sub.SortAndDisplayStations
$text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9102 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text $stations = get ship array: of race Player class/type=Moveable Ship gosub sub.FilterValidStations gosub sub.SortAndDisplayStations
$text = read text: page=$Page.ID id=2107 $input = create input: id='dropoff' menu=$menu title=$text description=$a.obj callback=null endsub
sub.DrawMineral: $default = $settings.table[$value] skip if $default $default = 0 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$value, value array=$aValues, default=$default, return id=$value, width=100 allowtabs=[FALSE] endsub
sub.JumpArray: $aValues = array alloc: size=26 $i = size of array $aValues while $i dec $i = $aValues[$i] = $i end endsub
sub.SortAndDisplayStations: if size of array $stations $stations = sort array $stations $i = 0 $size = size of array $stations while $i < $size $value = $stations[$i] $columns = array alloc: size=3 $text = $value -> get name $text = create custom menu column string, position=10 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $columns[0] = $text $text = $value ->create custom menu string object icon $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $columns[1] = $text $text = $value -> get sector $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=150 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $columns[2] = $text
add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$columns returnvalue=$value inc $i = end else $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=714 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$text end endsub
sub.FilterValidStations: $table = $settings.table['dropoff'] $i = size of array $stations while $i dec $i = $value = $stations[$i]
if $value == $a.obj remove element from array $stations at index $i continue end if $table[$value] remove element from array $stations at index $i continue end
do if $a.obj -> get amount of ware Freight Drone in cargo bay continue
if $value -> is of class Ship do if $a.obj -> get amount of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay continue do if $value -> get amount of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay continue end
if not $value -> is docking possible of $a.obj if not $a.obj -> is docking allowed at $value remove element from array $stations at index $i end end
end endsub
sub.GetSortedValidDropoff: $table = $settings.table['dropoff'] if not $table $table = table alloc $settings.table['dropoff'] = $table end
$next.key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $next.key $value = $next.key $next.key = get next key: table=$table key=$next.key end $array = sort table keys: table=$table endsub
sub.GetMinerals: $aMinerals = create new array, arguments=Ore, Silicon Ore, Ice, null, null do if $a.obj -> get amount of ware Mining Command Software in cargo bay append Nividium to array $aMinerals endsub return null
